inspiracio.servlet.http
Class IHttpServletRequest

java.lang.Object
  javax.servlet.ServletRequestWrapper
      javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequestWrapper
          inspiracio.servlet.http.IHttpServletRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
HttpServletRequest, ServletRequest
public class IHttpServletRequest
extends HttpServletRequestWrapper

Functionality that we add to javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest.

Invariant:

  • If request.getAttribute(ORIGINAL_COMPLETE_SERVLET_PATH) is set, it is the complete servlet path before any forwards.
  • If there has been a forward, it is set.
The class also provides setters for:
  • user principal: java.security.Principal
  • remote user: String
  • auth type: String
If they are not in this class, the getter returns whatever the wrapped object returns.

Field Detail

ORIGINAL_COMPLETE_SERVLET_PATH

public static final String ORIGINAL_COMPLETE_SERVLET_PATH
Store the original complete servlet path in a request attribute with this key. By "original" I mean, the URL before a forward. See class invariant.

The servlet path is stored a String. If it were a StringBuffer, a client could retain a reference to the StringBuffer and change its value from the outside. Strings are immutable.
